title: Converse Rubber Tracks: Oh, Hello - Redman
description:
This "Oh Hello" features rapper Redman as he praises his fans for pushing him to the next level, outlines what makes a successful artist and details his bathroom-based process for songwriting.
To learn more about Rubber Tracks visit:
http://www.converse.com/rubbertracks
